main event: A reported UFO sighting with an elongated, greenish object with some portholes observed.
interesting points: The object was described as elongated and had some portholes.
The object had an exhaust flame one and a half times the size of the object itself.
The sighting occurred on a clear night with good visibility.
The report comes from a reliable source, a 1st Lt. security officer.
There are no photographs or other visual evidence included in the report.
